dcterms:description: A dataset containing traffic collected over virtual private networks (VPNs), which are commonly used for accessing blocked websites or services. This traffic can be challenging to detect due to obfuscation technology.
dcterms:title: ISCX VPN-nonVPN

dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of traffic collected over the onion router (Tor), making its traffic difficult to trace, alongside a regular dataset not collected over Tor.
